      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm planning a trip and trying to pick a place to stay. if i'm looking for the best vibe, how would u compare a place like west highland (lots of old money, very quiet, safe) vs something like the east river district (lots of street life, diverse, more energetic)? which one would be considered more \"welcoming\" for a tourist just wandering around?",
